      ** ======
      *
      ** Error fields/message IDs/message data (arrays) from/to caller
     C                   PARM                    FldNamXAr
     C                   PARM                    MsgIDXAr
     C                   PARM                    MsgDtaXAr
      *
      ** Retail/GL Overrides - OK indicator
     C                   PARM                    DDRinoOK          1
